WEBVTT

00:01.133 --> 00:03.074
I just wanted to tell you
that I appreciate you

00:03.075 --> 00:04.275
patching things
up with him.

00:04.359 --> 00:07.862
I would do anything
for the woman that I love.

00:08.029 --> 00:09.530
They are gonna come at us
any way they can,

00:09.698 --> 00:10.948
and when they do,

00:11.083 --> 00:12.523
it's not gonna be
about heat sensors,

00:12.534 --> 00:14.034
it's gonna be about you.

00:14.119 --> 00:16.454
I know I'm not the only guy
in that company

00:16.538 --> 00:18.205
that knows
those sensors are faulty.

00:18.340 --> 00:19.780
I'm sorry, what is it
you need again?

00:19.808 --> 00:22.376
All the maintenance work orders
from the past six months.

00:22.461 --> 00:24.678
I can't let you have that
without authorization.

00:24.796 --> 00:28.215
Have you heard of the National
Transportation Safety Board?

00:28.350 --> 00:31.552
That's your secretary
unlawfully gathering evidence,

00:31.720 --> 00:35.389
which means there will be
no settlement of any kind.

00:35.557 --> 00:38.609
And tomorrow, I'm sending this
to the district attorney.

00:38.727 --> 00:41.979
Your whole story about how
Louis got his name on the door

00:42.063 --> 00:43.114
is bullshit.

00:43.231 --> 00:44.365
Jeff.

00:44.483 --> 00:47.451
It's over, Jessica.

00:47.569 --> 00:48.569
We're done.

00:55.243 --> 00:59.046
I can't believe you actually
got them to admit what they did.

00:59.131 --> 01:01.048
You better believe it,
because it's happening,

01:01.133 --> 01:04.501
and it wouldn't be
happening without you.

01:04.635 --> 01:06.420
You mean without me
being greedy.

01:06.505 --> 01:08.088
Joe, that's not
what I was gonna say.

01:08.256 --> 01:10.090
No, no, no, I know that
you don't think I care

01:10.258 --> 01:12.977
about these people,
but I do.

01:13.094 --> 01:14.428
But I'm also a working stiff.

01:14.596 --> 01:17.181
I go paycheck to paycheck
for my whole life,

01:17.265 --> 01:18.432
and then a thing like this--

01:18.567 --> 01:20.401
Could turn your
whole life around.

01:22.487 --> 01:25.105
Guy like you might not be
able to understand that.

01:26.575 --> 01:28.108
I understand.

01:28.193 --> 01:29.944
So it's a done deal?

01:30.028 --> 01:31.529
Might take a few
days to finalize,

01:31.613 --> 01:33.247
but yeah.

01:33.331 --> 01:34.949
It's happening.

01:35.033 --> 01:37.034
You have my word.

01:37.169 --> 01:38.452
You're all right, Mr. Ross.

01:44.626 --> 01:46.927
Harvey, you know the only
times you've been here at night

01:47.012 --> 01:48.295
were the god-awful
dinner party--

01:48.463 --> 01:49.463
And the other time.

01:49.464 --> 01:50.931
Well, this isn't that.

01:51.049 --> 01:52.299
I want to know
why Liberty Rail

01:52.434 --> 01:54.268
has a video of you
in their file room.

01:54.352 --> 01:55.519
What are you talking about?

01:55.637 --> 01:57.237
I'm talking the fact
that our smoking gun

01:57.355 --> 01:58.472
just became inadmissible.

01:58.640 --> 02:00.320
- Harvey--
- How'd you get those documents?

02:00.442 --> 02:02.193
Are you asking
if I did something illegal?

02:02.310 --> 02:03.394
Because I didn't.

02:03.478 --> 02:04.598
Well, they went to the D.A.,

02:04.613 --> 02:06.113
which means they think you did,

02:06.198 --> 02:07.898
so I'm gonna ask you
one more time,

02:08.032 --> 02:09.567
how did you get
in their file room?

02:09.651 --> 02:11.569
By walking through the
door they buzzed open.

02:11.703 --> 02:12.987
And why would they do that?

02:13.071 --> 02:14.154
Because I'm me.

02:14.289 --> 02:15.990
What the hell
does that mean?

02:16.124 --> 02:18.075
It means that I led
the woman to believe

02:18.159 --> 02:19.679
that I was an official
from Washington.

02:19.794 --> 02:21.161
Led them to believe it,

02:21.329 --> 02:22.663
or flat out told them?

02:22.797 --> 02:24.465
Because one kills our case

02:24.583 --> 02:28.919
and the other puts you
in a world of shit.

02:29.004 --> 02:30.137
Harvey, I'm not an idiot,

02:30.222 --> 02:32.022
and I don't appreciate
being treated like one.

02:32.057 --> 02:34.225
I told you I didn't do
anything illegal, and I didn't.

02:34.342 --> 02:35.559
Not an idiot?

02:35.677 --> 02:37.797
What the hell were you doing
there in the first place?

02:37.812 --> 02:39.452
- Harvey.
- It was Mike's idea, wasn't it?

02:39.481 --> 02:43.017
No, he didn't even
know about it.

02:43.151 --> 02:44.685
- Where are you going?
- To see Mike.

02:44.819 --> 02:46.687
I told you, he didn't even
know I was going to do it.

02:46.771 --> 02:49.356
I don't care, because he
sure as hell knew after.

02:49.441 --> 02:50.608
Let's go.

