03:01.002 --> 03:04.538
I am so proud of you.

03:04.706 --> 03:07.341
I've done that before.

03:07.425 --> 03:10.544
I'm not talking about that.

03:10.629 --> 03:12.096
I'm talking about your case.

03:12.213 --> 03:13.297
Ah.

03:13.381 --> 03:15.021
You believed in it,
and you fought for it,

03:15.050 --> 03:18.218
and I--
I love that about you.

03:18.353 --> 03:22.473
And I love that you
love that about me.

03:22.557 --> 03:25.059
When a person gives you
a compliment like that,

03:25.193 --> 03:27.061
you're supposed
to give one back.

03:27.228 --> 03:28.445
But I just did.

03:28.563 --> 03:30.403
I said that you love
that I love that about me.

03:30.482 --> 03:31.615
And what if I said I love
that you love that I love that

03:31.733 --> 03:33.317
about you?

03:33.401 --> 03:34.568
How would that make you feel?

03:34.736 --> 03:37.121
So tired.

03:37.238 --> 03:40.407
Well, we both know
why you're so tired.

03:40.542 --> 03:42.042
Yeah, because I'm so good.

03:42.160 --> 03:43.577
Don't you love that about me?

03:51.670 --> 03:53.710
You knew Donna bullshitted
her way into that company

03:53.755 --> 03:56.256
and you let us use
those work orders?

03:56.341 --> 03:57.474
How did you find out?

03:57.592 --> 03:58.926
It doesn't matter
how I found out.

03:59.094 --> 04:00.227
Answer my question.

04:00.312 --> 04:01.929
Yes, I knew, but what
difference does it make? We won.

04:02.063 --> 04:03.263
We didn't win,

04:03.348 --> 04:06.150
because Evan Smith has video
of Donna in their offices.

04:06.267 --> 04:07.434
- What?
- She know about this too?

04:07.569 --> 04:09.249
Harvey, she's just
trying to strong-arm us.

04:09.321 --> 04:10.437
Are you listening to me?

04:10.605 --> 04:12.272
They have the opposing
counsel's secretary

04:12.407 --> 04:14.274
poking around
in their goddamn file room.

04:14.442 --> 04:16.410
If I were the D.A.,
I'd sure as hell look into it.

04:16.528 --> 04:18.245
- The D.A.?
- Yeah, the D.A.

04:18.329 --> 04:19.613
Harvey, they let her in.

04:19.748 --> 04:21.588
According to you,
but they're gonna claim fraud

04:21.616 --> 04:23.334
or theft
or any number of things.

04:23.451 --> 04:25.085
What are you gonna do?

04:25.203 --> 04:27.454
I'm making a deal to drop this
case, that's what I'm gonna do,

04:27.589 --> 04:28.956
and you're gonna file
the paperwork as soon as I do.

04:29.090 --> 04:30.450
So you're just gonna
let this woman

04:30.458 --> 04:31.658
blackmail you without a fight?

04:31.710 --> 04:32.960
You're damn right I am.

04:33.044 --> 04:34.128
Harvey, we can still
win this case and clear--

04:34.262 --> 04:35.462
There is no case,

04:35.547 --> 04:37.297
and I wouldn't give a shit
about it if there was.

04:37.382 --> 04:38.632
I care about Donna.

04:38.767 --> 04:39.633
And you think I don't?

04:39.718 --> 04:40.718
You care so much for her?

04:40.769 --> 04:41.969
Then draw up those papers,

04:42.103 --> 04:44.304
because I'm letting
Evan know it's over.

