♪ Everybody wanna know
how it feel ♪

04:57.118 --> 05:00.237
♪ Everybody wanna see
what it's like ♪

05:00.372 --> 05:03.374
♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,
I don't mind ♪

05:03.491 --> 05:07.411
♪ Me and Missy is
so busy, busy making money ♪

05:07.545 --> 05:08.879
♪ All right ♪

05:08.880 --> 05:10.416
♪ All step back,
I'm 'bout to dance ♪

